4.text:
top = y - h
bottom = y + h
w2 = w * 2
h2 = h * 2
l = Math.round(h2 * 0.4)
m = 0
r2 = Math.floor((w2 - m * 3) / 8)
r = Math.round(r2 * 1.5)
k = Math.round(r * 2.3)
ar = Math.round(r2 * 0.8)
right = x + r2 * 2 + ar * 2
rpdm = right - ar * 2
rbok = rpdm - m
rc = rbok - r2
rgr = rbok - r2 * 2
lgr = rgr - m
lc = lgr - r2
lbok = lgr - r2 * 2
lpdm = lbok - m
left = lpdm - ar * 2
ln = lpdm - r2
hx = Math.round((lgr + rgr) / 2)
ttop = top + k
pdm = ttop + ar * 2
ph = bottom - l
ld = bottom - r2

5.text:
w = element.width / 2
h = element.height / 2
x = element.left + w
y = element.top + h

6.text:
circlePath(ctx, hx, top + r, r)
ctx.fill()

3.text:
ctx.beginPath()
ctx.moveTo(rpdm, ttop)
ctx.arc(
    rpdm,
    pdm,
    ar * 2,
    -Math.PI / 2,
    0
)
ctx.lineTo(right, ph)
ctx.arc(right - ar, ph, ar, 0, Math.PI)
ctx.lineTo(rpdm, pdm)
ctx.lineTo(rbok, pdm)
ctx.lineTo(rbok, ld)
ctx.arc(rc, ld, r2, 0, Math.PI)
ctx.lineTo(rgr, ph)
ctx.lineTo(lgr, ph)
ctx.lineTo(lgr, ld)
ctx.arc(lc, ld, r2, 0, Math.PI)
ctx.lineTo(lbok, pdm)
ctx.lineTo(lpdm, pdm)
ctx.lineTo(lpdm, ph)
ctx.arc(lpdm - ar, ph, ar, 0, Math.PI)
ctx.lineTo(left, ttop + ar * 2)
ctx.arc(
    left + ar * 2,
    ttop + ar * 2,
    ar * 2,
    -Math.PI,
    -Math.PI / 2
)
ctx.closePath()
ctx.fill()
